Revised R2 & R3

The system shall allow course registration until the official registration deadline. Late registration shall be permitted for up to 3 calendar days after the deadline with a late fee of $50.

Revised R5

The system shall prevent course registration when all seats are filled and shall provide an option to join the waitlist.

Revised R6

The system shall send an email confirmation to the student within 1 minute of successful course registration.

Revised R7 & R8

The system shall prevent registration if prerequisites are not met unless instructor approval is recorded in the system database.

Revised R9 & R10

The system shall prevent schedule conflicts unless one of the courses is fully online and asynchronous.

Revised R11 & R12

The system shall limit students to 18 credit hours per semester. Students may register for up to 24 credit hours only after advisor approval is recorded in the system.

Revised R14

The system shall charge a fixed fee of $100 for course drops made after Week 2 and before Week 6.

Revised R20

The system shall complete the registration transaction within 5 seconds under normal operating conditions.
